Merkel Says ‘Must Protect’ Euro States From Greece Predicament

-- B y   B r i a n   P a r k i n
-- 
2011-10-22T13:52:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-22/merkel-says-must-protect-euro-states-from-greece-predicament.html
German  Chancellor Angela Merkel  said
euro-region leaders must protect states including Spain and
 Italy  from suffering a similar predicament to  Greece , which
faces a restructuring of its bonds.  Speaking to the youth wing of her party of  Christian
Democrats  in the city of Braunschweig, Merkel said investors
face a deeper cut in the value of their Greek bond holdings and
the step poses risks of contagion. “We must prevent contagion,’
she said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Brian Parkin at 
 bparkin@bloomberg.net  